## Setup Instructions

### Requirements
```bash
pip install google-genai
```

### API Key
1. Go to [aistudio.google.com](https://aistudio.google.com)
2. Click **Get API key** → **Create API key**
3. Select a billing-enabled Google Cloud project
4. Export the key in your terminal session:
```bash
export GEMINI_API_KEY="your-key-here"
```

### Running the Script
```bash
python generate_synthetic_luganda.py
```

If interrupted, simply re-run — the script resumes from the last checkpoint automatically.

